{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I wound up executing the conception, and I probably prepared 800 to 1,000 documents for presentation and trial.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who was Kempner?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a German refugee, not Jewish, who had been state's attorney, whatever you want to call him, for the-- for Prussia before the Nazi accession to power, before '33.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is my understanding, although I didn't have that much contact with him-- I knew him, but we certainly weren't close.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were generations apart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He must have been every bit of 40 years old, which I thought was pretty damn old at this time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think he stayed in his office for the first year of the Nazi regime, into '34.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Prussia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was obviously out of favor because he wasn't a Nazi in any sense.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was I think neither a party member nor any kind of affiliate of the Nazis-- pretty good fellow, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know anything the matter with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, he came to the United States and lived somewhere in Pennsylvania for the rest of his life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he obviously was knowledgeable about German affairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He handled the von Weizsacker case, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't work with anybody hardly at all anywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked more outside on my own bailiwick with a fellow named Charlie Lyons-- Lyon, without an S-- who was a tax lawyer from Washington, probably responsible for my subsequent career.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just got along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a-- he was, I think, the principal prosecutor on the Flick case, which was a case against a German Nazi steel magnate who was convicted along with three or four of his colleagues in the Flick steelworks and who had a great career after the war.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He later became the owner of Mercedes-Benz, Daimler-Benz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
